description: This file defines a React functional component called Sidebar that renders a sidebar navigation menu for a surgery scheduling system frontend. It includes a brand section, navigation buttons for different sections (Calendar, Rooms, Resources, Device Status), and footer info.

methods.name: Sidebar({ active, onNavigate })
